claim.claim-text:
6. A light-emitting diode comprising: 
a light-emitting element; 
a reflecting substrate on which said light-emitting element is disposed; 
a cylindrical reflecting frame which is disposed on said reflecting substrate so as to surround said light-emitting element in a hollow portion of said reflecting frame; 
a fluorescent face made of a fluorescent substance containing a fluorescent material applied so as to surround said light-emitting element on an area defined by an inner circumferential surface of said reflecting frame and a surface of said reflecting substrate which is exposed from said reflecting frame.

8. A light emitting diode comprising: 
a light-emitting element; 
a reflecting substrate opposed to said light-emitting element and having a surface shaped like a paraboloid of revolution focused on the light-emitting element; 
wherein a fluorescent substance containing a fluorescent material is applied on the reflecting substrate to thereby form a fluorescent face.
